{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b8a61cba82","title":"有关“波匈事件”的言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5830ac519a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"b8a61cba82"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"d0fe9c9b0e","name":"厦门大学师生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"99a9448440","type":"title","text":"有关“波匈事件”的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"bfc3612ce3","type":"authors","text":"厦门大学师生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"afb6a1886b","type":"paragraph","text":"郑朝宗：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"42bfe3bd34","type":"paragraph","text":"“这次事件的发生，是由于格罗大骂请愿群众而引起。”(厦大快报5期)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"1085ab5801","type":"paragraph","text":"邓家余：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"7420903510","type":"paragraph","text":"“匈牙利事件发生的原因是：(1)匈牙利是苏军解放的，不是自己解放的，(意即革命是外加的)；(2)人民有过资产阶级(意即现在没有民主，太专政了)；(3)人民生活问题。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"d45a643701","type":"paragraph","text":"“从斯大林的铜象被拉下可以证明：匈牙利人民对苏联不满也是一个原因。总之匈牙利事件是苏联的压迫与剥削所引起的。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"09a863318a","type":"paragraph","text":"余兆升：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"ddc22116f1","type":"paragraph","text":"“匈牙利大学生在街头上参加暴动是对的，是争取民主；波兹南事件也是这样。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"9551918e12","type":"paragraph","text":"杨业金：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"27ad6f1ea4","type":"paragraph","text":"“事件发生是一党专政的结果。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"5e86cfde90","type":"paragraph","text":"物理系郑碧生：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"173c206711","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联出兵匈牙利，第一次为侵略，第二次为正义的。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"5c4be5649c","type":"paragraph","text":"历史系周铁耕：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"5b9cf5d54f","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联出兵匈牙利是干涉匈内政，对国际影响不好。匈牙利事件是好处多，坏处少。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"020c2ce16b","type":"subtitle","text":"历史系张再南：","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"c8c390b3f8","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联出兵是干涉匈牙利的内政。苏过分着急，待匈牙利快亡时出兵还来得及。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"aa28d5b883","type":"paragraph","text":"数学系郑锡宏：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"355feac699","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联出兵是干涉匈牙利内政；匈牙利和波兰事件主要是他们反对苏联在他们国家里的控制。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"ed8bbc3d79","type":"paragraph","text":"中文系郭铁链：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"d613abdf29","type":"paragraph","text":"“凡是有良心的人，都会说苏联出兵是不对的。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"72d2c0da11","type":"paragraph","text":"刘进颖：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"3e0e6ff15b","type":"paragraph","text":"“匈牙利的暴动是革命。”“苏联出兵是革命输出，是赤裸裸地干涉匈牙利内政。”“苏联应出志愿军，不应出国防军。”。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"60052561a9","type":"paragraph","text":"余兆升：","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"76c546d458","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联两次出兵都是干涉”，“苏联出兵是违反国际法的，为什么要外国军队镇压人民呢？”“苏联出兵是策略上的错误和政治上的失败。苏联在匈牙利的政治是失败的”。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"c88f36ec9d","type":"paragraph","text":"物理系刘贤容：","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"fbf4abdc32","type":"paragraph","text":"“波兰、匈牙利过去受苏联的不平等待遇。”","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"8cfdf99cc1","type":"paragraph","text":"数学系郑锡宏：","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"6177dad9ed","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联简直跟其他帝国主义一样，都在统治人民民主国家，这些人民民主国家跟殖民地一样，什么都要苏联同意才能做。”“东欧民主国家的共产党简直是乱七八糟，而且有严重的教条主义，什么都学习苏联，连半点民族自尊心都没有。”","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"d8f616fe24","type":"paragraph","text":"余兆升：","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"ecac1be99f","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联和人民民主国家的关系是帝国主义和殖民地的关系。”“人民民主国家没有独立性，和苏联一呼一应，成为苏联的傀儡。”","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"629a5aa696","type":"paragraph","text":"“真理报对铁托在普拉的演说的评论是断章取义，歪曲原意，纯碎是报复。”","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"f1bc9a771b","type":"paragraph","text":"“铁托的报告和南斯拉夫的管理制度很好，苏联偷偷地学它，中国也偷偷地学它。”","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"b283518ae1","type":"paragraph","text":"“铁托很大胆，敢于攻击苏共、阿尔巴尼亚劳动党以及法共和其领导人；其他人民民主国家总不敢。”","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"db6a094acc","type":"paragraph","text":"邓家余：","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"5adb8a2e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"“东欧人民反苏情绪高涨，拉科西是苏联指定的，匈牙利人民不要他做部长会议主席。”“东欧人民普遍对苏联不满”。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"6edf3a344f","type":"paragraph","text":"刘进颖：","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"514a7708e6","type":"paragraph","text":"“拉科西，格罗是饭桶；卡达尔也不高明”。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"2bf329a960","type":"paragraph","text":"“铁托的言论是理论上的问题，而且是国家领导人，我们(指人民日报)讲立场问题是扣他的大帽子”。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"},{"id":"a71196a51f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：中共厦门大学委员会宣传部编印《右派反动言论集》，1957年9月20日。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82"}],"page":{"id":"2df2448f87","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b8a61cba82","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}